  <h3>Overview</h3>
  <p>Bull City Food Growlers is a reusable take-out container program that aims to reduce waste and cost for local restaurants and improve the quality of life for Durhamites.</p>
  <p>Bull City Food Growlers are durable and long-lasting take-out containers which are 100% reusable. They can be washed and sanitized in commercial dishwashers. They are used in similar sustainable container programs across the country.</p>
